name: Christmas Girls Holiday Greeting Cards -  Assorted Pack of 15
description:
Christmas Girls Holiday Greeting Cards! Perfect for personal use or as a gift itself! 

The 15 card set features 3 designs (5 of each) illustrated and designed by myself, Nicole Alesi. (www.nicolealesi.com)

The inside of the card features a cute matching design that matches the front and reads: "Happy Holidays!"

Each card measures is 4.25" x 5.5" and is printed on high quality 12pt card stock with fine gloss finish. White envelopes are included. Watermark will not appear on actual cards

** You can also create a free online ecard or invitation to match courtesy of Pingg! Just visit my gallery: http://www.pingg.com/gallery/designer/nicole-alesi

The designs are also available for sale as individual packs of 20 - If you have any questions, please do not hesitate to ask. 

Happy Holidays!
